{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-95-amicable-chains","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 95: Lanac prijateljstva","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pravi delioci broja su svi njegovi delioci osim samog broja. Na primer, pravi delioci broja 28 su 1, 2, 4, 7 i 14. Pošto je njihov zbir jednak 28, taj broj nazivamo savršenim brojem.</p>\n<p>Iznenada, zbir manjih delitelja 220 je 284 i zbir manjih delitelja 284 je 220, čime formiraju lanac od dve brojeve. Zbog toga, 220 i 284 nazivaju se amikalni par.</p>\n<p>Možda postoji mnogo duži lanac. Na primer, počevši od 12496, kreiraćemo lanac od pet brojeva:</p>\n<p>$$\n12496 → 14288 → 15472 → 14536 → 14264 \\,(→ 12496 → \\cdots)\n$$</p>\n<p>Pošto ova lanca vraća na svoju početnu tačku, zove se kružna lanka.</p>\n<p>Pronađi najmanjeg člana najduže prijateljske lance bez bilo kog elementa koji prelazi <code>limit</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3cc1000cf542c50fede","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302212,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-95-amicable-chains"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function amicableChains(limit) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\namicableChains(300);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>amicableChains(300)</code> treba da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof amicableChains(300) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>amicableChains(300)</code> treba da vrati <code>220</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(amicableChains(300), 220);"},{"text":"<p><code>amicableChains(15000)</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>220</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(amicableChains(15000), 220);"},{"text":"<p><code>amicableChains(100000)</code> treba da vrati <code>12496</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(amicableChains(100000), 12496);"},{"text":"<p><code>amicableChains(1000000)</code> treba vratiti <code>14316</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(amicableChains(1000000), 14316);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-95-amicable-chains","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-96-su-doku","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-94-almost-equilateral-triangles","id":"5900f3cc1000cf542c50fede","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-95-amicable-chains"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}